  - abstract: In this survey I discuss A. Buium’s theory of “differential equations
      in the p-adic direction” ([8]) and its interrelations with “geometry over
      the field 𝔽₁”, on the background of various approaches to p-adic models
      in theoretical physics (cf. [1, 30]).
